      <title>因与伊朗的战争而被边缘化，加沙居民仍处于困境</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/world/middleeast/gaza-israel-mood.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的战争导致了加沙人的恐慌性购买和食品价格飙升，因为他们试图从以色列对哈马斯两年的攻势中恢复过来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/world/middleeast/gaza-israel-mood.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 09:59:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
