    <item>
      <title>伊朗战争中的能源攻击可能会将经济冲击转化为长期损害</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/business/economy/iran-war-oil-gas-global-economy.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[针对波斯湾石油和天然气基础设施的新阶段可能会对世界各地的企业和客户造成数月甚至数年的伤害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/business/economy/iran-war-oil-gas-global-economy.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 09:02:31 GMT</pubDate>
