    <item>
      <title>当选民担心“负担能力”时，许多人将矛头指向医疗保健</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/when-voters-worry-about-affordability-many-point-to-health-care.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管平价医疗法案相对受欢迎，但民主党在政治上取得的成功有限。现在，特朗普总统的医疗保健削减可能给这个问题带来了新的共鸣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/when-voters-worry-about-affordability-many-point-to-health-care.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 09:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
